Message.MsgText: EXCM_INVALID_PERMIT_ACTION_FORMAT=EXCM4001E: The following permit action format is not valid: {0} The system is expecting one of the following keywords, followed by a colon: Error, WRR, WLOR, or failover.
Message.Explanation: Permit action format was missing a keyword and/or a colon.
Message.UserResponse: Reconfigure the permit action to include a keyword followed by a colon.

Message.MsgText: EXCM_FILE_NOT_FOUND2=EXCM4003I: The file {0} was not found or was empty.

Message.MsgText: EXCM_PROP_NOT_SET=EXCM4002I: The property {0} has not been set.
